### Set Next.js Page Description Metadata

Source: https://github.com/vercel/next.js/blob/canary/docs/01-app/03-api-reference/04-functions/generate-metadata.mdx

This snippet illustrates how to define the `description` metadata field in Next.js, applicable to both `layout.js` and `page.js` files. The provided string value will be rendered as a `<meta name="description">` tag in the document's `<head>`, which is crucial for SEO and conveying page content summaries.

```jsx
export const metadata = {
  description: 'The React Framework for the Web',
}
```

```html
