## ✅ Subtask 4-6 Completed

**Created:** `src/app/datenschutz/page.tsx`

### Summary
- Migrated the datenschutz (privacy policy) page from the pages router to the app router
- Followed the exact same pattern as other migrated pages (impressum, lashlift, etc.)
- Used Next.js 15 `metadata` export for SEO instead of the legacy `Head` component
- Imports and renders the existing `DateschutzComponent`

### Changes Made
```typescript
import DateschutzComponent from "../../components/Datenschutz";
import type { Metadata } from "next";

export const metadata: Metadata = {
  title: "Datenschutz - Augenblick Chiemgau",
  description:
    "Augenblick Chiemgau - Wimperverlängerung Lashlift Traunreut Datenschutz",
};

export default function DatenschutzPage() {
  return <DateschutzComponent />;
}
```

### Verification
- [x] Page follows patterns from reference files
- [x] No console.log/print debugging statements
- [x] Clean commit with descriptive message (`cf00d3b`)
- [x] Subtask status updated to "completed"

**Note:** Browser verification at `http://localhost:3000/datenschutz` requires the dev server to be running with proper environment variables configured.

